            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EIn%20music%2C%20sounds%20that%20blend%20together%20are%20called%20harmony%2C%20or%20symphony.%20If%20individual%20tones%20and%20instruments%20do%20not%20blend%2C%20they%20clash%2C%20producing%20cacophony.%20Imagine%20the%20awful%20noise%20if%20all%20the%20instruments%20in%20an%20orchestra%20played%20their%20own%20notes%20in%20completely%20different%20keys!%20But%20when%20all%20the%20instruments%20work%20together%2C%20the%20result%20is%20a%20beautiful%20piece%20of%20music%20that%20uplifts%20the%20human%20soul.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGod%20has%20called%20each%20of%20us%2C%20with%20our%20individual%20tones%20and%20ministries%2C%20to%20blend%20into%20one%20body.%20The%20result%20will%20be%20as%20it%20was%20at%20the%20dedication%20of%20Solomon's%20temple%3A%20a%20beautiful%20display%20of%20unity-not%20one%20individual%20note%20or%20instrument%20that%20clashes%20with%20others%2C%20but%20a%20conscious%20blending%20of%20our%20gifts%20and%20callings%20with%20that%20of%20others.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPsalm%20133%3A3%20expresses%20it%20perfectly%3A%20%22Harmony%20is%20as%20refreshing%20as%20the%20dew%20from%20Mount%20Hermon%20that%20falls%20on%20the%20mountains%20of%20Zion.%20And%20the%20Lord%20has%20pronounced%20his%20blessing%2C%20even%20life%20forevermore%22%20(Psalm%20133%3A3).%20Whatever%20calling%2C%20church%2C%20or%20ministry%20we%20are%20involved%20in%2C%20we%20must%20walk%20in%20unity%20with%20everyone%20else.%20Then%20we%20can%20watch%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20our%20ministry%20multiply%20and%20see%20the%20glory%20of%20God%20displayed%20for%20a%20listening%20world.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
